{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2196489, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 425352, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "只想说干得漂亮，亚运会有电子游戏项目，就是个笑话", "timestamp": 1627962443, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2196497, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 425352, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "王者荣耀夹着尾巴好几年了还是当了冤大头", "timestamp": 1627962483, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2196499, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 425352, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "之前也批过几次，雷声大雨点小", "timestamp": 1627962488, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2196504, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 425352, "reply_to": 2196497, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 无论从哪个角度来讲，我觉得腾讯游戏都一点不冤。希望zf能有实际行动。", "timestamp": 1627962525, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2196525, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 425352, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "铁拳打向了手游，支持！国家整治这种暴利行业是好事", "timestamp": 1627962644, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2196559, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 425352, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "从QQ堂、QQ炫舞、QQ飞车、DNF的时代开始，我就觉得腾讯游戏一直是野蛮生长、只顾利益、社会责任感低下的，非常令人厌恶。", "timestamp": 1627962921, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2196653, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 425352, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "拨乱反正的时代要到来了！！！", "timestamp": 1627963742, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2196669, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 425352, "reply_to": 2196559, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 虽然但是我觉着腾讯（非腾讯游戏）总体来说社会责任的履行方面还OK吧，但腾讯游戏属实拉了胯…自己对tx系的游戏提不起来好感，属实是躺在流量上挣钱，重运营轻研发", "timestamp": 1627963944, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2196672, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 425352, "reply_to": 2196559, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 但不支持原文中说的游戏是“精神鸦片”的说法", "timestamp": 1627963967, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2196681, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 425352, "reply_to": 2196489, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 电竞那几年确实是向着规范化方向发展吧，虽然这几年看着像个笑话", "timestamp": 1627964020, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2196776, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 425352, "reply_to": 2196681, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 根本在于电子“竞技”不是运动啊，要上也是先走国际象棋一类", "timestamp": 1627964520, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2196800, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 425352, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "说实话，王者荣耀这种游戏，一个皮肤几十上百，还有两千块一个的荣耀典藏皮，属实离谱，垄断+暴利确实不合理\n别人3a也就几百块的价格，他不香？", "timestamp": 1627964761, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2196891, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 425352, "reply_to": 2196800, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 单说皮肤，本身对游戏性无影响，定价高本就属于奢饰品的范畴了。就好比买不起劳力士还骂它贵一样。\n不过垄断这一点确实有问题。\n另外，这篇文章的批评对象可是电子游戏，其中也包括你说的“3a”。", "timestamp": 1627965351, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 1715, "w": 1080}, "likenum": 2, "pid": 425352, "reply": 13, "tag": null, "text": "又一个行业要G了吗", "timestamp": 1627962258, "type": "image", "updated_at": 1627965349, "url": "zf/zfpzyi24hrsbybtlltjojp4iozzwykpl.jpeg", "vote": {}}}